			<p>Dynamic Movements Involved in the Impact The dynamic movements aren&rsquo;t so simple. There are three hand/arm/wrist movements occurring at the same time and they start in the middle of the downswing when the club reaches the right thigh and the shaft pointing around 9 o&rsquo;clock. The dynamic movements are basically finished by the time the arms reach 3 o&rsquo;clock on the follow through.</p>
