		<h2>Shots INTO the Wind</h2>
		<p>Take more club depending on the severity of the wind. It may be 1, 2, 3 clubs or more.</br> Swing easy with the club you choose.</br> Keep your balance.</p>
		<p>Shots DOWN wind:<br /> Take less club down wind decreases the amount of backspin on the golf ball so remember that the ball will roll more when it hits the ground.&nbsp;</p>
		<p>Off the tee shot&hellip;.&rdquo;Tee it high and let it fly.&rdquo;</p>
